Comment.Text: Targets 0-2 are the flickers, target 3 should be 'middle of the ship'

This scenario calculates the confusion matrix over several classes for SSVEP performance testing.
By default it loads the file specified for testing in the configuration scenario.
Note that if you use the same file for training and testing, the results are likely very optimistic.
n.b. The scenario does not test the numeric probability outputs that drive the Mind Shooter in the analog control mode. Only discrete control is tested.
